Subject: require checker secret on /api/feed/range

The range endpoint dumps a raw byte slice of the append-only log without
verifying the caller. Records belonging to other tenants surface inside
the returned blob. The endpoint is intended only for consistency checks
between the storage daemon and the feed sidecar; gate it on the shared
checker secret used by other internal endpoints.

